<title type="html"><![CDATA[1/16     airline / Why young Japanese aren't getting married(host:Howard)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=353&amp;p=369#p369"><![CDATA[
<span style="color: #00FFBF">************</span><span style="color: #FF0040"> <span style="font-weight: bold">Removal Notice</span></span> <span style="color: #00FFFF">!!!!!!!!!!</span><br /><span style="color: #BF0080">We'd like to inform you that the Thursday gathering of Royal English Club will be relocated with effective from Thursday , 16 Jan 2020. Details ae as follows:<br />Add:  Ikari Coffee<br />         100台北市中正區衡陽路114號<br /></span><br />Sesion 1<br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N61u-hneHFw" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N61u-hneHFw</a><br />Q1, What's the worst experience you flew ?  What's the ending?<br /><br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jBPc_MwfHyw" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jBPc_MwfHyw</a><br />Q2, What's  the worst / best airline you flew? Please consider the price to give it a fair evaluation.<br /><br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HovI0J62Oas" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HovI0J62Oas</a><br />Q3, Please share your experiences of flying traditional / budget airline. <br /><br />-------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 2<br /><a href="https://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2019/12/09/national/social-issues/parasite-singles-young-japanese-arent-getting-married/#.XhUdAFUzbe0" class="postlink">https://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2019/12/09/national/social-issues/parasite-singles-young-japanese-arent-getting-married/#.XhUdAFUzbe0</a><br />Why young Japanese aren't getting married<br />Q1. From this article , is there any different  thinking  between Japan and Taiwan?<br />Q2. Do you accept international marriage ? What if your daughter /son  falls in love with non-caucasian ( Vietnamese, Korean,Thai,Black,......), what's your opinion for him/her?<br />Q3. Do you agree that “would-be lovebirds  forget the finances and focus on Cupids arrow” as said in the article? Why or why not?<br />==========================================<br />Agenda<br />7:00 p.m. --7:30 p.m. Free talk<br />7:30 p.m. --8:10 p.m. First topic discussion<br />8:10 p.m. --8:40 p.m. Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited)<br />8:40 p.m.-- 9:15 p.m. Second topic discussion<br />9:15 p.m.-- <span style="color: #FF0000">9</span>:<span style="color: #FF0000">30</span> p.m. Presentation (Participants that haven't presented yet are invited)<br /><br />speaker time: 2 minutes for each speaker<br />host time: 3 minutes<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=13721">morris</a> — Fri Jan 10, 2020 2:44 pm</p><hr />
